kvůli Kwon Yulovi.

90
00:07:07,970 --> 00:07:09,810
Kwon Yulovi?

91
00:07:13,690 --> 00:07:15,970
To udělal Kwon Yul?

92
00:07:18,390 --> 00:07:22,610
Myslel jsem, že to víte, když jste tady,

93
00:07:25,450 --> 00:07:30,240
